SCHEMA: logistics/routing_rule.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.logistics.routing_rule
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic logistics routing rule declarations.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record routing_rule
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - rule_id: id
    - description: string
    - tie_break_policy: string
    - allow_multi_hop: bool
    - constraints: map
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- tie_break_policy must define deterministic ordering behavior.
